\f1\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Abstract\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 A system and method for providing contextual storytelling associated with digital media tracks within streaming platforms. Prior to playback of a selected media track, a short narrative segment is presented to the listener describing the origin, meaning, or context of the media. The narrative may be generated through multiple mechanisms including: original artist recordings, artificial intelligence generated voice likenesses of the artist, or compiled excerpts from historical interviews and recordings. The system includes verification mechanisms enabling artists to validate narrative accuracy, and playback controls allowing users to enable, disable, or repeat narrative segments. The invention improves listener engagement and contextual understanding of streamed media content.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Background\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Digital music streaming platforms currently provide access to large catalogs of media content but offer limited contextual storytelling related to individual tracks. Historically, artists have described song meanings through interviews, documentaries, or liner notes. These explanations are typically separated from the listening experience.\
As streaming services replaced physical media formats, contextual storytelling opportunities were lost. Existing platforms focus primarily on music playback and recommendation algorithms rather than providing narrative background.\
Additionally, advances in artificial intelligence enable generation of voice likenesses and synthesis of narrative content using historical data. However, current streaming services do not integrate such technologies into the playback experience.\
Therefore, a need exists for a system that integrates storytelling directly into streaming playback using artist recordings, curated archival material, and AI-generated narration.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

